Description: Combo of 3 Nautica Deodorants 150ml each (3*150ml)Nautica VoyageDrawing inspiration for aquatic tones and textures, Nautica Voyage for Men, is wonderful all-year-around scent. Fresh and salty like the sea breeze that carries scents of coastal herbs and woods, the concoction opens with green notes of leaves and apple moving into a heart of mimose, watery notes of lotus and accords of linen sail of a yacht, ending with base notes of cedar, moss, musk and amber.Nautica ClassicNautica by Nautica is a Woody Chypre fragrance for men. Nautica was launched in 1992. Top notes are aldehydes, lime, coriander, cypress, cinnamon, tarragon, clary sage, neroli, bergamot and lemon; middle notes are cyclamen, jasmine, caraway, rose and geranium; base notes are sandalwood, amber, patchouli, musk, oakmoss and cedar.Nautica BlueThe opening to Nautica Blue is both fruity and aquatic, and hits with some interesting notes. A lot of peach and some green grape, it's also quite creamy. As it dries, the traditional aquatic feel sets in, only it's still far more unique than Acqua di Gio's. The peach note manages to stay prominent, as it blends with a floral heart, and calone note. The base brings in some sandalwood and musk, and yes.. The peach is still there. In this fragrance's case, the end is anywhere from 6-8 hours later, as longevity is quite good. Especially considering its low price and it?s very popular amongst the fragrances.Nautica, a modern American classic, offers quality, design and value while capturing the essence of an active, adventurous and spirited lifestyle. Founded in 1983, Nautica has evolved from a collection of men's outerwear to a leading global lifestyle brand with products ranging from men's, women's and children's apparel and accessories to a complete home collection. Now part of VF Corporation, a leader in branded quality apparel, Nautica has become one of the most important American lifestyle brands throughout the world. Today the world of Nautica represents both a rediscovery and reinterpretation of what Americans have always wanted to wear. Nautica is currently available in more than 64 countries with more than 170 Nautica branded stores worldwide.
